$25 000 CIBC National Scholarship for Computer Science
Feb 01, 2005
math, uw, awards, waterloo, writing

- Awarded to applicants with outstanding scholastic standing, strong interpersonal skills, and entrepreneurial spirit
- Conditional on sustained academic performance

This provided me with an awesome opportunity to further my many passions, both technical and non-technical. It was also a much-needed exercise in writing meaningful application essays. If anyone from CIBC ever reads this:

Thank you.
